<div class="mycon" id="intro">
  <div class="introbox">

    <div class="intro-img-con">
      <%= image_tag "Homepage_bg_Island.png", class: "intro-ani", id: "island" %>
      <%= image_tag "Homepage_Title.png", class: "intro-ani", id: "title" %>
      <%= image_tag "wave.png", class: "intro-ani", id: "wave1" %>
      <%= image_tag "wave.png", class: "intro-ani", id: "wave2" %>
      <%= image_tag "wave.png", class: "intro-ani", id: "wave3" %>
    </div>

    <div class="cover">
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

<div class="mycon" id="block1">
  <div class="myrow-m">
    <div class="one-item">
      <div class="block1_intro"><p><br>「我們都是孤島，卻也同時座落在同片海洋。」<br></p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="myrow-m">
    <div class="block1_line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="myrow">

    <div class="two-item">
      <div class="block1_content">
        <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;凌晨一點,<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;我拖著疲憊的身子回到寢室,<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;大家都睡了。<br><br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;漆黑一片的寢室，<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;只有我桌上的檯燈還亮著。<br><br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;站在門邊望著遠處的書桌，<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;昏黃的燈光聚集，<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;像是一座孤島。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="block1_title1">
        <p><%= link_to '關於', '/pages/about#about-block1' %></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="two-item">
      <%= image_tag "Homepage_Icon_Island.png", class: "intro-img1" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="mycon" id="block1_1">
  <div class="myrow">
    <div class="two-item">
      <div id="block1-1img">
        <div class="intro-img2">
          <%= image_tag "Logo_CreativeClub.png", style: "width: 100%" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="two-item">
      <div class="block1_1_content">
        <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;孤獨  /<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/ 群島<br>
        <br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;當我們揚帆啟程，航向未知的遠方，<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;心理堅定的信念如北極星指引方向。<br>
        <br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;「總是會找到夥伴的。」<br>
        &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;因為每座島嶼，都屬於群島。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="block1_title2">
        <p><%= link_to '關於', '/pages/about#about-block2' %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

